      "beast_baseline": "i dont think i can do this anymore. every time i think i finally got things on track, i just end up right back here. same mistakes, same shitty jobs, same feeling of just being a burden to everyone. it feels like no matter what i change, the cycle just repeats. i'm just stuck in this loop and i'm so tired of fighting it.",
