      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "surrender to it? what does that even mean. like just sitting here letting it crush me? because honestly, that just feels like more of the same. it's like the more i try to fix things, the more i realize they're just broken for good. i feel like i've run out of options.",
      "beast_suffix": "",
