    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to accept \"being broken\" when the loop just keeps dragging me through the same shit. it feels less like acceptance and more like just waiting for the next disaster. if the cycle is just gonna keep repeating forever, then what's even the point of just existing like this? there's no real way to actually end the loop, is there?",
